Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we'll do both sides at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and then we'll go around the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.63,0:00:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, hi guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, hi all you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the Santa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:02:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these familiar faces, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Atkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who else did we miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all our famous, famous, familiar faces, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dermot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a wonderful lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a wonderful lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew she had a husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know who he was, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Dr. Atkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So good to see you, Dr. Atkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And Patty, God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are from Canada, in a different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's Marianne, our German translator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is Cornelia, the publisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's a physician, a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They do fasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And Michael DeBakey's wife is a patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it fasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it slow enough, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the best announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the last announcement is that Dr. Hawkins' new book,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending the Levels of Consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is available and in the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are a lot of copies for all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that haven't done all your Christmas shopping yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory and excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory be to God in the highest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And on earth, good will to men.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At Christmas time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace on earth, good will to men.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rest of it is so much tinsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But enjoyable tinsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're all children at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all children at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And you realize that on a Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the other thing perhaps of interest is this coming year, we've only seen it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only scheduled six of these all-day conferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,On the alternate month, every other Wednesday nights, on the alternate month,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the second Wednesday of the month, the second Wednesday of the month,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,on the alternate months, we'll meet informally at St. Andrews,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Episcopal Church Meeting Hall, 630 to 830, which means it'll probably be like six to nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It is absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's absolutely no charge, no cost involved, and we'll use the meeting hall there, which
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,will hold quite a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's an evening meeting for people who work during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people have moved to Sedona to be involved in the work, and so that will be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the core group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll be more classic satsang, you know, informal, and we'll just discuss questions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,at considerable depth, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's more or less for people who are somewhat sophisticated about the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really a class for beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This group here has advanced in consciousness to 100 points, 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This group, as a group, started at 400 and went up to 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rather nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So we start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the ego eventually discovers, the mind discovers that there's something beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The enthusiasm, the 300s, you tackle intellectual work, and then you discover that there's something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond mind, and that starts the spiritual quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual quest, classically, is difficult and not easy to do, and so, therefore, anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,who gets involved in spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I take my hat off to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's arduous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it less arduous is the purpose of writing Transcending the Levels of Consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it, to facilitate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're having it at St. Andrews, and the rector there, Mary Piotrowski, is very pleased
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to have us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've invited members of the congregation who wish to come over, come to the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It, because, classically, it's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm happy to be very pleased to have us, and I've invited members of the congregation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,who wish to come over, come to the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Classic Christianity, the reason I became an atheist was because of some of the characteristics
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of classic Christianity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got obsessed with sin and guilt and avoiding sin and being somewhat scrupulous
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,by nature, and obsessive compulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And have you ever heard of kings being a up to date instantly, or instead of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,difficult to live with within myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It created an invariable
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,tension. So
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity tells you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's wrong to hate your brother-in-law for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,screwing you over 30 years ago, but it doesn't tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,really how to get off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I said to Mary is this would be the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,practical, how to make
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, because
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a Christian church. If it was a Buddhist church
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd make Buddhism work, but anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,how to make a spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,ideal an experiential
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,reality, an experiential
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,reality. Experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to look at the ego is that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it is itself a virtual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no intrinsic reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but experiential
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it certainly seems to be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the only important
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,thing I want to decide today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We had great, wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and funny things happen. This
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,month's National Geographic magazine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is about Buddhism, December's
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,issue, and in it is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedona Tyron Auto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Outreach of Buddhism
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and it shows them praying in Sedona
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tyron Auto. Yesterday I was over there to get
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,what you would call a drive fixed up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said, wow, that's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were all excited about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, so Sedona,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, is sort of known as a spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,center. Where else would your
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tyron Auto be in National
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Geographic for having
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a meeting of Buddhists there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And some
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of the people in the picture had been to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,our classes. I could see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,people who had been to classes. There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedona Tyron Auto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's just what I wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,remind myself, St. Andrews.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lecture goes on to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,what is actually
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,chapters, I guess, 16 and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,17 in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth Versus Falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Religion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and spiritual, religious and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people are here for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to cover what we have to cover,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we won't have much time for the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to cover the basic materials as we
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,have in the past. I presume
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that people that are here have read
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and somewhat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,familiar with it. So we will only put up three or
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,four slides just
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to recall the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,structure out of which all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,arose. And
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say a few words about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology is only affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like having an altimeter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or a barometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a pragmatic
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,usefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you need
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to know via that mechanism, I've
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,done and written. There's nothing else you really need
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to know. So
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,revise how it originated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I attended a class on it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and an excellent teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,who wrote Your Body Doesn't Lie
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,he was a great teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I went back to the clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and had a very large holistic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,holistic orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Largest psychiatric clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Largest psychiatric practice in the United
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,States for some 25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,years. So we looked for everything that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,could possibly help a patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Misdiagnosis. So we
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,were open to every kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,alternative medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And we had
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,considering our patient population
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of hopeless that had already seen everybody in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,recoveries were
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,indeed miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came back to the staff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and demonstrated kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought we could find, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can find out whether your
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,psychosis is due to mercury
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,poisoning or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes, I'll tell you how long it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a diagnosis that all the world's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,experts can't make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got mercury poisoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's got mercury poisoning
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in the brain. So if we chelate him out, he'll
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,recover. That's how
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,long it takes. That's how long
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes. It's very, very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so there's no point
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a big deal out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology then is just a mechanism
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that corroborates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,what people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,once the third eye of the booty body
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,opens up, all that you learn through
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can look at the image of somebody on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,television, the nightly news,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can look at his face and I'll tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,what he calibrates right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to have this guy around
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The word killer emerges in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you find out, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he killed four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He claims he's innocent, but the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,knowingness is that he's not innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so it's useful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,for research. It's useful for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,corroboration. It is not
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,essential to enlightenment at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it doesn't work for you, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We are
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,planning to do a teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,on it. It's going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,done by
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,our staff here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief of staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have her do that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that's enough for kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very simple thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people that are experts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,at it. I'm not an expert at kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know nothing about it. I just know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,true or false. That's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes or no. That's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There are experts at it, and they have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,video tapes that are wonders to behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there's all kinds of tricks. You go
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,like this, and the guy goes weak. And you go like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and he goes strong. And you go like this, and he goes strong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's very complicated. I am not
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a kinesiologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't claim to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know is truth and falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth makes your arm go strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and falsehood makes your body go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has to do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with brain physiology and the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is an infinite field.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is an
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite field.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a priori
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,prior to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,within the physical domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which is infinitely powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,arises all of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the Godhead
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,arises divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,whose expression is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In seeing that, you see that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,creation and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That evolution is creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think it was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,going to look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But from
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing to everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but everything isn't complete yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,still in a progression.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, to really see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that evolution and creation are one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and the same thing makes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it easy. The other thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to see right from the beginning and save yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,many years of many lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is that everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is occurring spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,as a consequence of that which
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it is. There is no
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,external cause for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything manifests
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,its own potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,when local conditions are favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The caterpillar
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes the pupa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes the butterfly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,etc. Nothing is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,causing anything to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,at all. Now there's
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,a reason I always try to keep track
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of what's going on in science too,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I know what I'll forget
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,when I go over to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The first book I wrote was called
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth vs. Falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth vs. Falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was called
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Power vs. Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The years are going by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Called Power vs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So the statement I just
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,made, we said
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,force goes from here to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's limited and it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausts itself. It has to be fed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,constant energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Power, the effects of power
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,are the consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which power
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is. Power just stands
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there and does nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and influences everything
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a bit of difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,then is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's powerful and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it radiates out and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,things around it change as a consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's a new
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,scientific theory
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrated at 480
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I could read this guy's name
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirokapos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-A-R-O-K-A-P-O-S
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A new scientific theory
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,supplanting Newton
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that motion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in the universe is not the result
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of force
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but of power. Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That the power
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which radiates out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of the essence of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,manifests
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:19:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,become stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can also think
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and be intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a link.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You follow Newtonian
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to quantum mechanics
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the Heisenberg principle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what did I say his name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirokapos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Einstein was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirokapos
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 480
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and Newton's theory
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is about 450.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Newton's
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,concept of causality
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is about 450, 455.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Newtonian science
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 450
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and this guy is at 480.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's worth noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming closer and closer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that you wouldn't be able
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to live the day without
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing about Mr. Hirokapos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing of interest
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep you up to date
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,on what's happening
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is the US doesn't calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest of all the countries
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Singapore is at 440.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Singapore is the consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of a benign dictatorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to Brock,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is this a friendly dictator?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they all have to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,torture people to death
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and fry them and rape them
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Brock did the research
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and came up, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Singapore emerged out of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a benign, very enlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and Singapore calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,at 440.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the US
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is still at.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at 421.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at 422.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,423.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The United States is at 440.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,421.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,420.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll get you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in the ballpark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We mentioned that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,informal meetings
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you want the dates
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll be on the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,website.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give them to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,An interesting thing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,going on in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of significance
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is the recent meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Islamic nations,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,35 of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,led by King Abdullah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of Saudi Arabia
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.05,0:22:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to renounce the violent
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,extremism that is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,really a negation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of the basic teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of Islam.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.13,0:22:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they're getting together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and saying, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.34,0:22:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that kind of violence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and all is a distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we took care
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.93,0:22:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of all the important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't attire an auto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,on Heracopolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we'll continue
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as we usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We now are up to about 75 slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of an oversized book
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think with the slides
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,on this side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and a page of explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,on this side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because it recapitulates
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,everything in the easiest way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts off with a map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,over great periods of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.55,0:23:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So the calibrated scale
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is pragmatic, useful,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and frankly we can find out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,things within an instant
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact some of it was published
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in Truth vs. Falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We held it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.72,0:23:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,though it was safe to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a lot we did not say
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in Truth vs. Falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that the public wouldn't be able
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But practically everything we said
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there has emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, all the food scandal,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,all the things that showed up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,on the radar a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's extremely useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now in translating the levels
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.98,0:23:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,from a psychological, spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,emotional viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,showed how to transcend each level.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.29,0:23:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a practical how-to manual
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.29,0:23:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.38,0:23:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:24:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,let's go on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's familiar with that slide
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody understands that slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.83,0:24:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And we go into it in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.83,0:24:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This brings up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.33,0:24:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,interestingly another law
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.33,0:24:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which I had overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.38,0:24:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In Italy there was an economist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.38,0:24:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an economist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.53,0:24:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an economist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.85,0:24:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Paretta
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.77,0:24:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Paretta
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.77,0:24:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody, any Italian economist?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.91,0:24:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Paretta
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the late 1800s
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,he discovered that 80% of the land
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.03,0:24:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in Italy was owned by 20% of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.03,0:24:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And he set up what's known
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.35,0:24:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as the law of 2080.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.35,0:24:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably 80% of the stock
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.80,0:24:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.80,0:24:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is owned by 20% of the stockholders.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.86,0:24:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,80% of the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.86,0:24:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is owned by 20% of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.94,0:24:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just discovered that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.94,0:24:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,this weekend and I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.94,0:24:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.94,0:25:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.94,0:25:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Practically the same
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.94,0:25:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as we've been talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.94,0:25:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for some years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.94,0:25:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Practically the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.94,0:25:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Approximately 20% of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.15,0:25:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,then
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.27,0:25:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,has the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.27,0:25:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.27,0:25:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the 78%.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.27,0:25:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay so we go to the next thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.44,0:25:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending the levels
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.84,0:25:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.00,0:25:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,was really I wrote it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.00,0:25:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,at Susan's
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.00,0:25:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.00,0:25:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept saying you need
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.00,0:25:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to explain things practically.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.00,0:25:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,People were interested in the practical how to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.14,0:25:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And so at her inspiration
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.14,0:25:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and urging we did it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.14,0:25:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm glad I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.14,0:25:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So here you got Paretta's law
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.14,0:25:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,approximately
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.14,0:25:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you know when he says 2080 he means approximately.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.14,0:25:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Approximately
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.25,0:25:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,one-fifth
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.42,0:26:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,wags the tail of the four-fifths.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.11,0:26:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay so we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.33,0:26:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just to recall
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.33,0:26:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of the world we live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.33,0:26:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature of the world we live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.59,0:26:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To get off feeling guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.72,0:26:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,about the ego we just
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.72,0:26:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I always like to recall how it evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.72,0:26:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Life appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.98,0:26:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,when
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.54,0:26:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions were favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.54,0:26:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of divinity when it interacted
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.54,0:26:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,with matter spawned
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.54,0:26:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy fuel called life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.54,0:26:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Life only can originate from life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.54,0:26:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Life
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.22,0:26:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,can only originate from life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.22,0:26:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.31,0:26:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Life can only
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.79,0:26:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,originate from life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.79,0:26:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Life can only originate
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.82,0:26:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,from life. It cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.82,0:26:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,originate from non-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.44,0:26:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You never saw a dead animal get up and start to bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.44,0:26:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.44,0:26:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Life emerges from life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.44,0:26:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes care of
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.47,0:26:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,mechanistic reductionism.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.47,0:27:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.43,0:27:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get you up there where they can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.94,0:27:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh mechanistic reductionism.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.94,0:27:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good golly. No wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.94,0:27:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the microphone blew out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.34,0:27:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.79,0:27:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we see this is the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.79,0:27:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.79,0:27:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was essential
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.79,0:27:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to life. So when life
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.79,0:27:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,spawned out of matter
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.79,0:27:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.79,0:27:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity, the energy fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.79,0:27:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in the form of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.79,0:27:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in its interaction with matter
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.79,0:27:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,spawned life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.18,0:27:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to survive life
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.18,0:27:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,had to become predacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.18,0:27:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It had to have like laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.18,0:27:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,test equipment biologically
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.18,0:27:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell what's edible, what's not edible,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.18,0:27:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what's good for life,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.18,0:27:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what's adverse to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.43,0:27:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology is a subtle
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.43,0:27:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,form of it. That which is pro-life
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.43,0:27:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,supports life and makes you go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.43,0:28:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.43,0:28:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,anti-life does not support
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.58,0:28:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,life and makes you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.94,0:28:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first organization
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.94,0:28:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of humanism already discovered this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.94,0:28:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of that arose
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.94,0:28:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that aspect of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.94,0:28:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,we call the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.94,0:28:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiencer samples
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.94,0:28:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,everything around is it safe, not safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.94,0:28:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,edible, non-edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.49,0:28:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So then we see the evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.22,0:28:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,through great eons of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.22,0:28:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the whole animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.22,0:28:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.38,0:28:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,from the very lowest level
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.38,0:28:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the bacteria is still the very
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.38,0:28:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,lowest we could find at one
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.38,0:28:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,protozoa and then
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.38,0:28:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,on up through the animal kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.38,0:28:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,my favorite friend
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.38,0:28:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the octopus,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.57,0:28:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the Komodo dragon, you just don't want to hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.57,0:28:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.99,0:28:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be sure
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.11,0:28:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to put your shoes on when you go into
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.11,0:28:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the Komodo dragon's cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.25,0:28:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we come up
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.41,0:28:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,through the whole animal kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.41,0:29:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and we come up from
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.41,0:29:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that which sort of survives
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.41,0:29:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,by
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.41,0:29:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the death of others
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.41,0:29:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and we come up to the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.41,0:29:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,benign herbivore.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.41,0:29:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This occurs at calibration
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.47,0:29:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,level 200 in the animal kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.47,0:29:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the same as it does
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.47,0:29:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in the human kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.59,0:29:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The human kingdom is the same
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.59,0:29:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,as the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.59,0:29:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200 is predacious
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.59,0:29:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and above 200
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.59,0:29:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is peaceful and herbivorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.59,0:29:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we come up
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.21,0:29:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to the exceptional things.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.21,0:29:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the family dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.21,0:29:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We know research shows
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.21,0:29:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that having a pet
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.21,0:29:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,increases all the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.21,0:29:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,good aspects of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.21,0:29:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Healthier, better heart function,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.55,0:29:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,less suicide rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.02,0:29:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's enormous benefits
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.02,0:29:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in having a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.22,0:29:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So then
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.96,0:30:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we get up to the higher levels
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.96,0:30:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the monkeys, the gorillas
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.96,0:30:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we get up to the very high levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.96,0:30:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The African parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.18,0:30:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.18,0:30:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,how is broccoli doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.18,0:30:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see how broccoli, broccoli
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.18,0:30:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is over
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.50,0:30:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,wow, broccoli's over 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.24,0:30:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli's over
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.61,0:30:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,385.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.72,0:30:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli's over 380.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.72,0:30:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,385.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.75,0:30:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli's up to 380.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.46,0:30:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Got nowhere to go yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.46,0:30:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.48,0:30:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sitting at home all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.48,0:30:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden broccoli gets on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.48,0:30:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.48,0:30:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry I gotta go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.48,0:30:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes it sound like the phone's going off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.48,0:30:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.64,0:30:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligence there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.81,0:30:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Intelligence, intelligent design.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.81,0:30:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The intelligence in the design
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.01,0:30:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is so obvious you've got to be
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.01,0:30:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,retarded to reject
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.01,0:31:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligent design
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.01,0:31:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as a basic principle of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.01,0:31:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you really gotta be dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.01,0:31:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really dumb to not see
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.01,0:31:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.21,0:31:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, here's a parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.21,0:31:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to you and you don't see the intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.21,0:31:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, then you got Coco
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.33,0:31:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course the dog
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.33,0:31:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.46,0:31:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It represents some emanation
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.46,0:31:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,very similar to the human heart at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.46,0:31:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.54,0:31:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So that covers again the very basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.54,0:31:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.54,0:31:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to feel guilty about the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.54,0:31:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.54,0:31:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,domesticate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.54,0:31:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.71,0:31:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because here is the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.71,0:31:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,big shift in brain function
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.71,0:31:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that occurs at consciousness level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.71,0:31:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.90,0:31:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in faulting people
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.90,0:31:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.57,0:31:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,are
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.66,0:31:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,non-integrous
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.66,0:31:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,because their brain simply
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.66,0:31:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.70,0:32:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Their brain simply doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.50,0:32:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The skeptic
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.51,0:32:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.68,0:32:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't get here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.68,0:32:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because there isn't any etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.68,0:32:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't process.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.02,0:32:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't see the spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.02,0:32:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.57,0:32:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,over 200
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.57,0:32:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that there's intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.57,0:32:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,intrinsic to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.79,0:32:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,information is so
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.79,0:32:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,stunningly obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.79,0:32:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's stunningly obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.11,0:32:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But to people with this kind of a brain
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.11,0:32:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.11,0:32:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They are stuck with mechanistic
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.11,0:32:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,reductionism.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.53,0:32:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not specific
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.53,0:32:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,if I can't identify it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.53,0:32:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.59,0:32:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You see this because here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.59,0:32:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we're dealing with different energies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.59,0:32:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with etheric energies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.73,0:32:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At consciousness level 200
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.73,0:32:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is the emergence of the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.73,0:32:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.10,0:33:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And individual karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.29,0:33:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Below level 200
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.83,0:33:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,there's group karma
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.83,0:33:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and above 200 is individual karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.83,0:33:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.83,0:33:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure they didn't change it while I was out for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.83,0:33:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just said is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.00,0:33:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.45,0:33:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.48,0:33:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,People below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.05,0:33:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,are coming in here with a group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.08,0:33:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore you see major group
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.08,0:33:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.08,0:33:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole cultures get wiped out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.08,0:33:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,volcanoes, tornadoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.08,0:33:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.08,0:33:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole groups get wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.63,0:33:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.63,0:33:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Individual karma then
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.61,0:33:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is based on the etheric energy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.61,0:33:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the etheric body.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.20,0:33:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fix that microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.20,0:33:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, help, help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.35,0:33:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, help, help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.35,0:33:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.59,0:34:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Instant karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.60,0:34:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.44,0:34:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain physiology
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.44,0:34:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you see it's easier to forgive people.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.44,0:34:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Man can only
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.69,0:34:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,choose the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.11,0:34:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He perceives that as the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.11,0:34:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So killing you is what he
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.11,0:34:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,perceives as the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.11,0:34:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He still is operating from the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.17,0:34:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you forgive people
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.17,0:34:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.17,0:34:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it by realizing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.17,0:34:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize between Socrates
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.17,0:34:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and this chart that takes care of the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.17,0:34:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,resentment, forgiveness, hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.40,0:34:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.40,0:34:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got any hatreds left?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.40,0:34:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Resentments? Blames?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.55,0:34:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Any blamers? Let's hear blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.73,0:34:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Blame. Blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.86,0:34:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what's wrong with this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.09,0:34:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the effing blamers out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.09,0:34:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.69,0:35:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a righteous blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.17,0:35:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now neatly
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.11,0:35:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind can
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.11,0:35:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,pull us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.26,0:35:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All blames are terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.26,0:35:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,except the righteous blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.26,0:35:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All wars are terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.26,0:35:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,except the righteous war.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.26,0:35:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Righteous blame. Righteous resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.26,0:35:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.42,0:35:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need this kind of apparatus
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.42,0:35:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to process
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.42,0:35:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and to bypass emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.42,0:35:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You need an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.42,0:35:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See here, the animal emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.42,0:35:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is very rapid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.42,0:35:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got an emotional reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.42,0:35:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's in your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.42,0:35:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How he screwed you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.42,0:35:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The SOB 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.78,0:35:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see him differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.78,0:35:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He only did what he thought
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.78,0:35:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he had to do
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.78,0:35:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's who he was at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.78,0:35:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And now very fast you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.78,0:36:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.78,0:36:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.78,0:36:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you become over 200
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.78,0:36:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that differentiates
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.78,0:36:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a major step in evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.07,0:36:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.65,0:36:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.65,0:36:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is sort of recapitulating
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.65,0:36:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for the new people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.65,0:36:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't reinforce this often enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.65,0:36:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.65,0:36:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is not due to anything out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.65,0:36:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be coming from cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.71,0:36:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's coming from essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.71,0:36:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.71,0:36:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.90,0:36:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,directly aligned
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.90,0:36:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with your level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.90,0:36:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and not anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.00,0:36:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.61,0:36:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to live on Millionaire's Row
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.61,0:36:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and they committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.61,0:36:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and got drunk and got divorced
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.61,0:36:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and killed each other
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.73,0:36:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the same as everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.73,0:36:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't seem to help much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.86,0:36:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't seem to help much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.86,0:36:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So happiness then is not caused
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.86,0:36:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,by conditions out there
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.86,0:37:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,any more than unhappiness is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.86,0:37:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhappiness or happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.92,0:37:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.92,0:37:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.50,0:37:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.61,0:37:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll have completed pretty much the prelims.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.61,0:37:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.88,0:37:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we're getting to the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.88,0:37:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,lecture for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.01,0:37:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say it's covered in
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.15,0:37:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,chapters 15 and 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.15,0:37:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The last two chapters I think
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.15,0:37:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of truth versus falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.19,0:37:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In which
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.09,0:37:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we discover sort of a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.09,0:37:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,practical
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.38,0:37:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,sense of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.38,0:37:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and we begin to use it to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.59,0:37:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,analyze everything
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.59,0:37:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in history and in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.59,0:37:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we use it to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.59,0:37:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,understand theology
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.59,0:37:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and religion
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.59,0:37:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.36,0:37:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So we start out then
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.65,0:37:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the world religions
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.65,0:37:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the so-called sons of Abraham.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.65,0:38:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.94,0:38:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Islam,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.94,0:38:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Judaism.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.03,0:38:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Which came out of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.03,0:38:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,historically out of Abraham.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.38,0:38:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they've been
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.82,0:38:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,having difficulties with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.82,0:38:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since but
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.30,0:38:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the basic idea
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.44,0:38:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,was alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.44,0:38:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just the way it was applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.73,0:38:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we start now
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.86,0:38:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,looking to see what
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.17,0:38:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,scale of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.17,0:38:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How do all these things calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.21,0:38:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the better we understand things
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.21,0:38:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the better we can integrate them
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.21,0:38:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,accept them and also
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.21,0:38:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,get off making things wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.21,0:38:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The first century of Christianity
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.07,0:38:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the way
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.13,0:38:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the first followers of the way
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.13,0:38:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,are calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.13,0:38:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,at 980.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.78,0:38:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The apostles all calibrated in the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.78,0:38:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,900s.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.78,0:39:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The very high 900s.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.26,0:39:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The relics, the Saint Peter under the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.26,0:39:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.32,0:39:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Peter's yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.15,0:39:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the relics anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.15,0:39:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The relics calibrate over 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.15,0:39:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very unusual
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.15,0:39:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the relics of Saint Peter under the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.38,0:39:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's under the altar
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.38,0:39:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Basilica of Saint Peter's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.38,0:39:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.44,0:39:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates over 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.44,0:39:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So the apostles calibrated 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.44,0:39:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now many centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.44,0:39:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,later they discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.44,0:39:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the writings of the Gnostics
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.44,0:39:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.44,0:39:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,at 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.44,0:39:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the interesting thing about Christianity
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.82,0:39:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is prior to the Council of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.82,0:39:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicaea it calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.82,0:39:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.09,0:39:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And after the Council of Nicaea
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.09,0:39:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it dropped considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.09,0:39:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It dropped from
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.78,0:39:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.90,0:40:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,prior to the Council of Nicaea
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.90,0:40:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity was at
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.90,0:40:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,840.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.90,0:40:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Council of Nicaea
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.90,0:40:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in 325 AD
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.90,0:40:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it had dropped to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.90,0:40:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,485.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.07,0:40:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.07,0:40:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just get myself from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.25,0:40:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.53,0:40:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this rig still going?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.61,0:40:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.84,0:40:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It dropped to 485.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.84,0:40:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most catastrophic thing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.88,0:40:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,other than what happened with Muhammad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.03,0:40:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.03,0:40:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is powerfully
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.03,0:40:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,virtuous and truthful
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.03,0:40:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,pulls to it all its enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.30,0:40:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like truth becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.86,0:40:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,such a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.13,0:40:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,danger to falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.13,0:40:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that falsehood pulls itself up
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.13,0:40:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and sneaks in the door somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.13,0:40:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.73,0:40:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,he was beset by demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.73,0:40:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And in my own
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.01,0:41:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.38,0:41:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was beset by demons
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.38,0:41:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and then some.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.46,0:41:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's though
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.46,0:41:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's said you pull up its opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.46,0:41:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You tend to pull up its
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.50,0:41:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the enemies of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.26,0:41:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.30,0:41:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the enemies of truth cleverly
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.30,0:41:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,conceal themselves in sheep's
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.30,0:41:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.53,0:41:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment, the opening of the third eye
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.53,0:41:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is the capacity to see
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.53,0:41:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the wolf under the sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.53,0:41:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So at the council
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.26,0:41:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of Nicaea then
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.57,0:41:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened I believe is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.57,0:41:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the way the Bible
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.88,0:41:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,came about was really
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.88,0:41:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there were many
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.88,0:41:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,books of the Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.21,0:41:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the books are not in the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.21,0:41:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,current Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.55,0:41:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They met periodically and voted on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.55,0:41:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very extensive
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.73,0:41:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,history. The history of the Bible of course is very
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.73,0:41:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,extensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.73,0:42:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not a religious historian.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.73,0:42:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't give you the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.73,0:42:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know what did happen
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.73,0:42:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Old Testament got included
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.73,0:42:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with the New Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.96,0:42:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and Revelations got included
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.28,0:42:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in the New Testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.78,0:42:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And that brought it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.46,0:42:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In the New Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.19,0:42:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened was the introduction
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.19,0:42:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of that particular book which
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.19,0:42:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates it 90 or 70 or something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.19,0:42:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,brought down the calibration
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.19,0:42:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,level of the whole New Testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.19,0:42:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And brought down Christianity
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.19,0:42:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,prior to the council of Nicaea
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.96,0:42:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,840
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.96,0:42:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,after the council of Nicaea
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.96,0:42:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,485.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.96,0:42:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's something for religious
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.96,0:42:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,historians to
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.96,0:42:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,puzzle out. I myself
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.96,0:42:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,don't know that much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.90,0:42:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Catholicism then
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.90,0:42:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is Eastern Orthodox
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.15,0:42:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Coptic and Roman Catholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.15,0:42:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eastern Orthodox
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.15,0:43:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,currently calibrates about 490
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.15,0:43:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,which is higher than it would
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.15,0:43:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Council of Nicaea.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.15,0:43:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Coptic is at 475.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.15,0:43:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And Roman Catholicism
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.21,0:43:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of course has been the dominant
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.21,0:43:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity for many centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.21,0:43:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Papacy
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.34,0:43:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,itself calibrates at 570.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.34,0:43:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The last Pope
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.34,0:43:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated at 570.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.34,0:43:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This Pope calibrates about 565
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.34,0:43:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,between 565 and 570
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.34,0:43:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,which is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.34,0:43:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,a small variation
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.34,0:43:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and not particularly relevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.34,0:43:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So we found that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.34,0:43:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,570 is ideal for the head of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.34,0:43:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,a world church, the Dalai Lama
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.34,0:43:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,also calibrates at 570.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.34,0:43:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Above 570
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.36,0:43:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't really handle
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.88,0:43:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the worldly things that have to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.88,0:43:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,be handled. Below 570
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.09,0:43:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have the power
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.09,0:43:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to withstand the attack
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.09,0:43:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes to you just by virtue of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.09,0:43:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.19,0:43:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Papacy
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.90,0:44:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,at 570
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.90,0:44:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,has withstood the test of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.90,0:44:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There were several Popes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.90,0:44:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.90,0:44:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,notorious ones, who calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.90,0:44:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,well below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.57,0:44:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say they were false Popes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.38,0:44:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A poor Pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.46,0:44:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fake Popes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.11,0:44:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The College of Cardinals
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.11,0:44:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you see is very erudite at 490.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.11,0:44:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,490 is really about
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.11,0:44:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as the intellect will take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.21,0:44:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The faith and liturgy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.21,0:44:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,this comes out of the intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.21,0:44:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but faith and liturgy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.21,0:44:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,comes out of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.21,0:44:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and again you're back over 500
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.21,0:44:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to 535.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.98,0:44:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith and liturgy then
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.98,0:44:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the main core
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.98,0:44:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.32,0:44:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.86,0:44:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The clergy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.19,0:44:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,also calibrate around 490,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.19,0:45:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the Jesuit order.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.48,0:45:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The church worldwide,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.48,0:45:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Catholicism is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.48,0:45:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,currently around 450,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.48,0:45:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.40,0:45:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is far above 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.40,0:45:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's had difficulties
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.82,0:45:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and straightened out
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.82,0:45:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the difficulties
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.92,0:45:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which will probably bring
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.92,0:45:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,its calibrations back up
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.92,0:45:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,higher again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.32,0:45:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, post reformation
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.32,0:45:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.90,0:45:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so what happened was
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.90,0:45:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got the church
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.90,0:45:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,world dominant
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.73,0:45:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there was complaints
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.73,0:45:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,complaints about
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.92,0:45:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,errors made, ecclesiastic errors
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.92,0:45:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and that started the reformation
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.96,0:45:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of the post reformation
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.96,0:45:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then you see
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.96,0:45:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,many of the most prominent
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.96,0:45:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,religions in America
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.96,0:45:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.96,0:45:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the Amish at 375
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.96,0:45:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,born again Christians
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.96,0:46:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Christian Science
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.96,0:46:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Episcopalian
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.11,0:46:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,this is where we're going to be meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.11,0:46:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,on the alternate months
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.28,0:46:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelical
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.28,0:46:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fundamentalist Christian
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.28,0:46:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,LDS
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.57,0:46:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and New Thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.51,0:46:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After post reformation
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.65,0:46:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you have Pentecostal
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.65,0:46:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Protestantism
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.65,0:46:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 510
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.65,0:46:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Protestantism
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.65,0:46:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 510
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.86,0:46:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Puritans
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.86,0:46:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other hand
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.86,0:46:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,seem to be overly moralistic
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.86,0:46:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they didn't quite do quite as well
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.09,0:46:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Quakers are very peaceful people
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.61,0:46:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Making it all real
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.61,0:46:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in the everyday world
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.61,0:46:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Salvation Army at 405
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.80,0:46:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and Unity Church
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.80,0:46:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 500
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.80,0:46:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Unity Village itself
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.80,0:46:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 500
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.86,0:46:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and we of course
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.86,0:46:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,have had the pleasure of being there
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.86,0:47:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a number of times as their guest
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.86,0:47:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and being on the advisory council
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.90,0:47:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of Unity Church's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.90,0:47:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,work on
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.98,0:47:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.98,0:47:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.07,0:47:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity then
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.07,0:47:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is about one third of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.07,0:47:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in America it's certainly a sizeable
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.07,0:47:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and now we see
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.07,0:47:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the resurfacing of course
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.07,0:47:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of the whole contention about Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.07,0:47:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,which is pretty ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.07,0:47:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.21,0:47:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it gives contentious people something to do
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.21,0:47:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and protest about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.84,0:47:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you're really hard up
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.84,0:47:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,for something to protest about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.84,0:47:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when you've got to pull up Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.84,0:47:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,from the bottom of the basket
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.84,0:47:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to pull up Santa Claus
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.26,0:47:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and beat him up
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.42,0:47:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you're really getting down there
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.42,0:47:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all the little children
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.42,0:47:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.96,0:47:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.96,0:47:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what's our favorite Christmas movie
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.96,0:47:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stooge
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.88,0:48:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.88,0:48:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Scrooge
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.92,0:48:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah the Scroogeites
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.92,0:48:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,come out of the woodwork
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.17,0:48:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,can you imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.17,0:48:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in your death bed
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.17,0:48:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you know you're going to face God any second
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.36,0:48:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the problem with life
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.46,0:48:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is too many people
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.46,0:48:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,are too far from death
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.65,0:48:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,those of you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.90,0:48:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,who've had near death experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.90,0:48:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,know what I'm talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.26,0:48:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,all this BS
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.26,0:48:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,drops away like the stupidest crap in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.26,0:48:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and there you are
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.86,0:48:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,facing the infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.86,0:49:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and when the ego goes out
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.09,0:49:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you know it went out
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.09,0:49:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when I gave up life itself
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.86,0:49:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and walked through the door
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.86,0:49:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it also gave up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.86,0:49:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the near death experience
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.09,0:49:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very similar
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.09,0:49:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when you turn off the TV at night
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.09,0:49:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the screen just goes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.09,0:49:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,like that and disappears
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.46,0:49:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,well that's the way it is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.46,0:49:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,everything all your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.46,0:49:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,everything you ever thought
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.46,0:49:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,all of your history
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.46,0:49:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,means
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.01,0:49:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,what strikes you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.01,0:49:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is the fantastic
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.01,0:49:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the pomposity of it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.01,0:49:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the pomposity of it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.01,0:49:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,like an idiot trying to tell the king
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.01,0:49:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how to run the government
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.40,0:49:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,alright yes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.40,0:49:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.57,0:49:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the idiocy of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.96,0:49:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so then you learn
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.76,0:49:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to take it with a grain of salt
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.76,0:50:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and realize it is a virtual reality
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.76,0:50:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in today's world
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.76,0:50:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we have
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.86,0:50:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the downside is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.86,0:50:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the media
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.86,0:50:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the programming by the media
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.86,0:50:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is so staggering
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.86,0:50:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,promotion
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.86,0:50:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,advertising
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.46,0:50:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,politicalization
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.71,0:50:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the modern man
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.71,0:50:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,when I grew up you could live a whole lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.71,0:50:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,where I grew up
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.71,0:50:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you could live a whole lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.96,0:50:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe read the headlines once in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.96,0:50:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't need to know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.96,0:50:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,about the world
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.96,0:50:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and who was interested anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.19,0:50:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it was harvest time
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.92,0:50:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it was hay time
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.92,0:50:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it was planting time
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.92,0:50:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,who cared about that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.01,0:50:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to fix the brakes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.01,0:50:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,on the 29 model a Ford
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.01,0:50:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and they wanted six dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.15,0:50:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,my father called them highway robbers
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.15,0:50:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,six dollars to replace the brakes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.15,0:50:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in today's world
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.59,0:51:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.94,0:51:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,at the mercy of an input
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.94,0:51:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that is overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.94,0:51:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.40,0:51:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,people give me gadgets sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.40,0:51:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I always take out the instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.40,0:51:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have a drawer full of gadgets
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.40,0:51:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,people have given me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.40,0:51:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with the instructions still with them
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.46,0:51:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a letter to the editor said
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.46,0:51:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,today's technology has gotten so advanced
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.46,0:51:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that things are becoming almost useless
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.46,0:51:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes two to three hours
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.46,0:51:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to read the instruction manual
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.46,0:51:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you sort of give up
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.46,0:51:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave up years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.46,0:51:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if it doesn't just go off and on
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.46,0:51:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.38,0:51:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,off and on
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.38,0:51:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Susie's pretty good at that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.61,0:51:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,she can handle a
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.61,0:51:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,SUV
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.61,0:51:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you know in a new car
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.61,0:51:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I counted there are 100
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.61,0:51:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,switches from the driver's seat
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.61,0:51:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you need that one for transporting
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.57,0:52:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.01,0:52:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat in it and I counted them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.01,0:52:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,there are 100 switches
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.78,0:52:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it does mysterious things
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.78,0:52:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you're counting the switches
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.78,0:52:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden you see
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.78,0:52:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the mirrors changing around you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.78,0:52:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the rear view mirror is going in and out
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.78,0:52:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,this seat is pulsating
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.19,0:52:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,your back is going like this
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.19,0:52:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,vibrational things
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.19,0:52:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then a voice comes out of the roof
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.48,0:52:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of the car and speaks to you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.98,0:52:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it's time to change your oil
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.98,0:52:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to Susie
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.98,0:52:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus I didn't know you were supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.98,0:52:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to put oil in this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.98,0:52:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that's Christianity
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.90,0:52:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of which we're all familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.90,0:52:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in the non-Christian world
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.90,0:52:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it's familiar as well
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.44,0:52:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,then the second great wing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.44,0:52:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we could start with the oldest wing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.44,0:52:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Judaism
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.44,0:52:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we should have started here
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.44,0:53:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because historically
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.44,0:53:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of course it predates all the others
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.44,0:53:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.44,0:53:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Judaism has withstood
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.44,0:53:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all the ravages of time
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.44,0:53:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Judaism is really
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.57,0:53:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for a stand-up religion
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.57,0:53:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been shot at
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.57,0:53:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,bombed, exploded
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.57,0:53:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,drowned, stabbed
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.57,0:53:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and it still goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.57,0:53:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasidism is 605
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.57,0:53:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely high
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.57,0:53:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasidism
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.57,0:53:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is the conscious awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.57,0:53:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of the divinity of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.57,0:53:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the constant reminding yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.57,0:53:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of the divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.57,0:53:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.57,0:53:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Messianic includes
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.57,0:53:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the inclusion of Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.57,0:53:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.57,0:53:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,also a 605
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.57,0:53:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as a great prophet
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.57,0:53:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or as a representative of God
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.57,0:53:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Reconstructionist
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.57,0:53:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,conservative
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.57,0:53:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the Jewish people
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.80,0:53:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.80,0:54:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,conservative or reform
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.21,0:54:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,conservative or reform
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.59,0:54:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and orthodox
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.59,0:54:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,at 545
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.59,0:54:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so you see
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.59,0:54:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Judaism stands out extremely well
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.59,0:54:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it has stood up over the centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.82,0:54:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,despite everything
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.82,0:54:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.82,0:54:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's a very high level of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.19,0:54:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself had millions of Jewish friends
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.19,0:54:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,back East
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.19,0:54:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I even got to do the Seder
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.19,0:54:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the service
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.19,0:54:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,they gave me a yarmulke
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.19,0:54:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had a white thing over me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.19,0:54:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I sat there and read the whole service
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.19,0:54:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it was wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.19,0:54:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,then we went to a fantastic place for dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.86,0:54:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower East Side
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.86,0:54:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,traditional Jewish dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.03,0:54:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it started at 7, 10.30
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.03,0:54:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we were only up to about the 6th or 7th course
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.03,0:54:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it was great
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.17,0:54:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so I learned to love
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.17,0:54:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the people
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.34,0:54:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,now Islam
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.34,0:54:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is the most recent one
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.34,0:54:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course it only arose
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.92,0:55:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time of
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.92,0:55:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Muhammad
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.92,0:55:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Muhammad
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.61,0:55:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,stated that he got it as
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.69,0:55:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of a dictation
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.69,0:55:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Archangel Gabriel
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.01,0:55:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,at that time Muhammad was at 700
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.01,0:55:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Quran
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.38,0:55:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the original Quran calibrated at 700
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.82,0:55:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he was at age 35
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.82,0:55:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,age 35
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.57,0:55:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,at age 38
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.90,0:55:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he crashed from 700
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.55,0:55:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to about 185
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.94,0:55:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or something
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.94,0:55:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,he had temporal lobe epilepsy
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.28,0:55:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,temporal lobe epilepsy
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.63,0:55:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is peculiar
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.63,0:55:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it often has religious delusions
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.63,0:55:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and various
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.82,0:55:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,problems with it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.82,0:55:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.92,0:56:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so Muhammad at 700
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.92,0:56:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,dictated the original Quran
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.36,0:56:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in this version
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.40,0:56:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is what I said
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.40,0:56:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is powerfully for the good
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.40,0:56:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,pulls its enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.40,0:56:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and its enemy came at him
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.40,0:56:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and it came through the temporal lobe epilepsy
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.40,0:56:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,subsequent to which
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.40,0:56:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,he became warlock
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.40,0:56:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,warlike
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.88,0:56:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and Islam
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.88,0:56:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,fell dramatically
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.92,0:56:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,however
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.50,0:56:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the original truth
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.50,0:56:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is maintained by the mystics
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.71,0:56:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the Sufism is at 700
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.71,0:56:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in all religions
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.71,0:56:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the mystics are always calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.71,0:56:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.73,0:56:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have today's Sunnites
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.73,0:56:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and Shiites
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.73,0:56:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,at about 250
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.42,0:56:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the difficulty with Islam
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.42,0:56:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was the emergence
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.42,0:56:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,first of all
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.42,0:57:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of Muhammad's great fall
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.17,0:57:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.17,0:57:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,130 it was
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.17,0:57:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he took up the sword
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.17,0:57:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the difficulty was
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.17,0:57:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in mistranslating the Quran
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.17,0:57:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual sword
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.82,0:57:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,means the sword of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.82,0:57:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I came not to bring you peace
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.01,0:57:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but to bring you truth
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.01,0:57:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the sword of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.01,0:57:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to mix up the sword of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.30,0:57:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,with the sword of war
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.30,0:57:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.30,0:57:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in the misinterpretation of the Quran
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.30,0:57:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.86,0:57:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.26,0:57:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayyid Khattab
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.42,0:57:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and Wahhab
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.63,0:57:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,are the two things that brought it down
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.63,0:57:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wahhabism emerged
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.63,0:57:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,300 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.90,0:57:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and a misinterpretation of the Quran
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.90,0:57:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and the further decline
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.53,0:57:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,was supported by
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.53,0:57:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a famous author named
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.19,0:58:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayyid Khattab
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.19,0:58:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,he wrote a book called
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.19,0:58:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the shades of the Quran
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.80,0:58:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in which all that goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.80,0:58:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in today's Islamic terrorism
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.80,0:58:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,was justified
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.57,0:58:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and it eulogized
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.57,0:58:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and praised death
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.57,0:58:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,death
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.57,0:58:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,death and destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.40,0:58:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so that when you see
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.40,0:58:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bin Laden who was a follower
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.40,0:58:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of Wahhabism
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.55,0:58:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he calibrates at 90
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.78,0:58:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I calibrated his lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.78,0:58:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in which he says
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.78,0:58:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the difference is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.19,0:58:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you worship life
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.19,0:58:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and we worship death
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.19,0:58:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that calibrates at 90
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.32,0:58:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to worship death
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.32,0:58:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.32,0:58:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so that is the basic
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.32,0:58:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the basic problem
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.32,0:58:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Islamic terrorism
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.32,0:58:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,colors everything
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.32,0:58:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't think it's important
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.34,0:58:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,just go to the nearest airport
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.34,0:59:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you got to take your shoes off
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.34,0:59:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you got to wait in line
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.34,0:59:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they can take everything away from you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.34,0:59:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it's totally changed our world
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.48,0:59:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so having nothing to do at all
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.48,0:59:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with the basis of it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.48,0:59:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it still has changed our world
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.76,0:59:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so Islam then
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.76,0:59:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sufism
