Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.73,1:07:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,eat at Joe's barbecue
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.73,1:08:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you're getting programmed even when
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.46,1:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you're what
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.46,1:08:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,your guard's down
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.01,1:08:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you gotta go and there you are
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.21,1:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you just got programmed
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.90,1:08:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,did anybody ask you
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.90,1:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.30,1:08:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so you see the basic innocence of the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.42,1:08:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the basic innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.42,1:08:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the ego in and of itself
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.42,1:08:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is unable to discern truth from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.93,1:08:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.93,1:08:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,res interna versus res externa
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.93,1:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,res interna is the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.90,1:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you see the world
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.90,1:08:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,res externa is the way the world is
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.90,1:08:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the way the world is
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.30,1:08:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's an intrinsic dichotomy
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.30,1:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's almost impossible
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.48,1:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,for people under 200
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.48,1:08:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's impossible
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.48,1:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to see the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.48,1:08:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the way it is
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.48,1:08:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore culpability is different
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.48,1:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200 and over 200
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.77,1:08:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,culpability below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.77,1:09:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is that of ignorance
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.81,1:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore as you get over 200
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.81,1:09:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to be a little more meticulous
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.81,1:09:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because now you're
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.81,1:09:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,answerable and culpable
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.81,1:09:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you're no longer considered
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.81,1:09:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a spiritual idiot
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.81,1:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the good news
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.81,1:09:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll save the bad news
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.14,1:09:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for later
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.14,1:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so the interaction
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.46,1:09:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of these three things is today's world
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.46,1:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is it not
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.46,1:09:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Israel, Judaism
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.46,1:09:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,people say I don't like it if you mention politics
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.46,1:09:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,why?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.46,1:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because politics is the secular fallout
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.46,1:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of religion, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.77,1:09:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,all of politics is nothing but religion
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.77,1:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got its expression
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.77,1:09:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,within the world
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.77,1:09:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so in doing truth versus falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.77,1:09:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that was the purpose in chapter 9
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.77,1:09:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to go through the world
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.90,1:10:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of its details
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.90,1:10:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Eiffel Tower
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.90,1:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to political parties
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.52,1:10:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to elections, whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.84,1:10:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and see how does this
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.84,1:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,filter out in everyday world
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.84,1:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's one thing as an abstract theory
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.84,1:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's another thing
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.84,1:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,how does it actually filter out in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.84,1:10:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so these are the sons of Abraham
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.84,1:10:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,how they filter out
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.84,1:10:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody got any questions
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.84,1:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because then we're going to take a break
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.84,1:10:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody got any questions about
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.84,1:10:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,what we've said
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.84,1:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we might as well handle it now
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.84,1:10:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrations up there
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.84,1:10:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,are they the current practices of those churches
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.84,1:10:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ask
