Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.84,1:10:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Catholicism has to be updated a little bit
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.84,1:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because they went through a whole thing about
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.84,1:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,clergy pedophilia and all that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.84,1:10:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and probably came back up again now
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.84,1:10:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ask what is the level
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.84,1:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of a current day church worldwide
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.84,1:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,let's do
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.38,1:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,College of Cardinals
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.38,1:10:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to ask what I'm asking
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.31,1:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.85,1:11:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvary is over 485
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.85,1:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.85,1:11:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvary is over 490
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.23,1:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.23,1:11:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvary is over 488, 489
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.27,1:11:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,College of Cardinals currently
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.27,1:11:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,488
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.77,1:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that's pretty high erudition
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.28,1:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,488 is very high erudition
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.28,1:11:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,488 is very high erudition
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.64,1:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not stupid
