Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.64,1:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,any other questions
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.64,1:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,when someone falls
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.64,1:11:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,they're above 200
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.64,1:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and they fall below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.98,1:11:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,do they still have an etheric brain
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.98,1:11:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and individual karma
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.98,1:11:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.05,1:11:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,gee that is a question
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.72,1:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a person is over 200 and they fall below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.72,1:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so they fall to the point where they have an etheric brain
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.72,1:11:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we can ask this question
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.85,1:11:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,now they make a very bad choice
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.85,1:11:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,choose that which is non-integrous
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.85,1:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and they fall
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.97,1:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the etheric brain remains resistant
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.97,1:12:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,disappears it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.47,1:12:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,they pull the plug
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.81,1:12:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say it's a certain radiation
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.88,1:12:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then when that radiation is not there
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.88,1:12:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it disappears
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.88,1:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a radiation
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.88,1:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you know we get all kinds of emails and letters
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.88,1:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and gifts and things
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.88,1:12:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and before I open the package I got what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.88,1:12:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you get the radiation of it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.88,1:12:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you get the energy precedes it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.88,1:12:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it's dead
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.88,1:12:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I say let's calibrate it before we open it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.88,1:12:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure it's ok to open
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.01,1:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes we just put it in the dumpster
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.48,1:12:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,would that person notice the loss
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.18,1:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,would that person notice the loss
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.18,1:12:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know sweetheart
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.65,1:12:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never killed anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.14,1:12:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.38,1:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine you'd feel pretty dejected
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.38,1:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.38,1:12:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I should say so yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.85,1:13:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why some people turn to drugs too
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.85,1:13:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because they were in a high place
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.85,1:13:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,they made a bad choice
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.85,1:13:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and now drinking drugs gives them a certain state of artificial euphoria
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.85,1:13:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.21,1:13:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason the 12 step program works
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.21,1:13:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is you've got the euphoria without the drug
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.21,1:13:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.21,1:13:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,all you were seeking all along was the euphoria
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.21,1:13:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.21,1:13:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,sobriety tends to persist
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.21,1:13:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah anybody else
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.21,1:13:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.21,1:13:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,another term for that would be radiant
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.85,1:13:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,another name for what
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.72,1:13:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a radiance
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.56,1:13:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.56,1:13:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the radiance of divinity within
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.50,1:13:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the radiance of divinity within
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.48,1:13:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it's exhibited by
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.64,1:13:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you have become
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.64,1:14:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,determines
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.85,1:14:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.03,1:14:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,need not say
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.81,1:14:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,anything
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.34,1:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,position thusly in the current
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.34,1:14:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you automatically rotate this way
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.53,1:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,effortless
