Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.39,1:14:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,at 480
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.81,1:14:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,things are not a consequence of
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.97,1:14:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of causation
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.97,1:14:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but of power
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.69,1:14:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because of the power
