Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.47,1:14:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.47,1:14:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you draw to yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.47,1:14:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is aligned with divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.89,1:14:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the miraculous
