Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.53,1:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,why not
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.14,1:15:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to go a day
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.06,1:15:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without a miracle happening
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.06,1:15:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't we have a miracle yesterday
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.94,1:15:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,she's still weeping from it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.02,1:15:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you get
