Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.22,1:15:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in the high 500s
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.22,1:15:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you're crying all the time
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.22,1:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you know you're in the 500s
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.22,1:15:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to calibrate yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.65,1:15:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.65,1:16:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just a cry baby
