Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.93,1:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,from anything I would call
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.93,1:16:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,an other
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.10,1:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with the exception
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.10,1:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was in the pits of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.10,1:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and I asked God for help
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.23,1:16:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got hit by a huge energy
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.23,1:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which I think was an archangel
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.35,1:16:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it was
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.73,1:16:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it was
